ty.nebulas.io/assets/files/2019-01-09/1547019797-295047-017c5d554909920000019ae9d202fejpg-at-1280w-1l-2o-100sh.jpeg\">[upl-image-preview url=https://community.nebulas.io/assets/files/2019-01-09/1547019797-295047-017c5d554909920000019ae9d202fejpg-at-1280w-1l-2o-100sh.jpeg]</UPL-IMAGE-PREVIEW></p>\n</r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'103.22.200.129',0,1),(49,16,2,'2019-01-09 09:54:41',114,'comment','<t><p>Nebulas NOVA 和之前已上线主网的鹰星云最大的区别在哪里？NOVA上线主网后，鹰星云又会何去何从？两个主网，一种token，数据是怎么流转的？这两者关系有点让人云里雾里。。。</p></t>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'173.245.48.228',0,1),(50,16,3,'2019-01-09 10:28:09',65,'comment','<r><p><POSTMENTION discussionid=\"16\" displayname=\"llp\" id=\"49\" number=\"2\" username=\"llp\">@llp#49</POSTMENTION></p> \n\n<p><POSTMENTION discussionid=\"16\" displayname=\"llp\" id=\"49\" number=\"2\" username=\"llp\">@llp#49</POSTMENTION> nova是鹰星云升级后的2.0版本，相对于1.0鹰星云新增了，NR,DIP,NBRE等全新特性</p></r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'172.69.33.104',0,1),(51,17,1,'2019-01-09 10:46:51',36,'comment','<r><p>Want to know about Nebulas? Desire to get information? <br/>\nYou can see the tutorial here, you can get what you want step by step <URL url=\"https://community.nebulas.io/t/education\"><s>[</s>here<e>](https://community.nebulas.io/t/education)</e></URL>&gt;.&lt;!!!<br/>\n Of course, you can also provide information to others as a teacher.</p>\n \n<p>Let<FP char=\"’\">\'</FP>s learn together!!!</p></r>','2019-01-09 12:10:44',36,NULL,NULL,'172.68.211.157',0,1),(53,18,1,'2019-01-09 11:54:09',36,'comment','<r><p>Here you can discuss things about Nebulas Community board. Want it to upgrade? Improve something? What features do I need to add? Can the composition be adjusted?</p>\n\n<p>Give us a suggestion!</p>\n\n<p>We can discuss it together. After all, our community is precious and needs to be given the best. We have to keep it together in the best state <E>:)</E></p></r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'172.68.46.170',0,1),(54,11,5,'2019-01-09 12:29:34',36,'comment','<r><p>Sooooooooo  super exciting! and I<FP char=\"’\">\'</FP>m looking forward to talking with you!!!!!!!!!</p></r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'172.68.211.61',0,1),(55,19,1,'2019-01-09 12:31:19',36,'comment','<r><p>Hi, there! This is xixiu from Nebulas, I<FP char=\"’\">\'</FP>m so glad that we can share more creative and valuable ideas here &#128578;<br/>\nLet<FP char=\"’\">\'</FP>s make some great things together in 2019! Go Nebulas!</p></r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'172.68.211.61',0,1),(56,16,4,'2019-01-09 12:40:58',36,'discussionStickied','{\"sticky\":true}',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1),(57,20,1,'2019-01-09 13:05:27',70,'comment','<r><p>On this Thursday, January 10 from 7PM to 8PM, 2019 (PST), Nebulas team will hold a live Ask-Me-Anything (AMA) on Nebulas Community Forum, with the topic of <FP char=\"“\">\"</FP>Nebulas Incentive Program on Nebulas NOVA Testnet<FP char=\"”\">\"</FP>. During the AMA, Nebulas founder Hitters Xu and Nebulas Research Institute director Dr. Xuepeng Fan will give a detailed explanation on the rules and details about Nebulas NOVA Testnet Developer Incentive Program.</p>\n\n<p>Community members are welcome to sign up in our forum and leave your questions first, also you can discuss with community members all over the world. Furthermore, to encourage community members to join in this AMA, the Nebulas team will select 10 participants with constructive ideas, and reward each of them with 5 NAS!</p></r>','2019-01-11 02:36:54',36,NULL,NULL,'103.22.200.189',0,1),(58,20,2,'2019-01-09 13:08:18',36,'discussionTagged','[[11],[11,26]]',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1),(59,11,6,'2019-01-09 13:12:42',80,'comment','<r><p>I think Nebulas is great!  <FP char=\"–\">--</FP> Nakamoto</p></r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'162.158.118.229',0,1),(60,16,5,'2019-01-09 13:31:00',36,'discussionTagged','[[15],[15,24]]',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1),(61,11,7,'2019-01-09 13:32:04',36,'comment','<r><p><POSTMENTION discussionid=\"11\" displayname=\"Nakamoto\" id=\"59\" number=\"6\" username=\"Nakamoto\">@Nakamoto#59</POSTMENTION> I DO T