','[\"This is our own tech forum! ASK these phD. everything here!\",\"This is our own tech forum! ASK these Ph.D. everything here!\"]',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1),(166,20,32,'2019-01-11 04:41:38',136,'comment','<r><p><POSTMENTION discussionid=\"20\" displayname=\"JakubNY\" id=\"149\" number=\"16\" username=\"JakubNY\">@JakubNY#149</POSTMENTION> Thank you for your question. Nebulas is one of the earliest Chinese public blockchain projects that has reached out to the overseas community. We also have a lot of supports from overseas.  Therefore we will maintain our focus on the overseas market. The testnet of Nebulas NOVA has already been released, and in our market plan of 2019, we will put more attention on the overseas market, including delivering more PR articles and also paying more attention on developers community. We will also try to apply ATP on-chain advertisement to better improve the performance of our overseas market and operation.</p></r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'108.162.245.67',0,1),(167,20,33,'2019-01-11 04:45:14',136,'comment','<r><p><POSTMENTION discussionid=\"20\" displayname=\"Mista-Mist\" id=\"148\" number=\"15\" username=\"Mista-Mist\">@Mista-Mist#148</POSTMENTION> Thanks for your questions. We have put in extensive efforts on the research and development of the underlying infrastructure of Nebulas, and it does not mean that we pay less attention in building the ecosystem or marketing.</p>\n\n<p>As a public chain project, we have always been holding strong with respect to the market, and it<FP char=\"’\">\'</FP>s hard for any single project to beat the entire market condition. Nebulas keeps forging ahead to complete our promises and goals, and we hope our community could join us together to make Nebulas better.</p>\n\n<p>In terms of our ecosystem development, our key target is to introduce incremental “token users” to our ecosystem and thus to create a sustainable and sound ecosystem. We have incubated the first benchmark protocol layer application Atlas Protocol and as a on-chain advertising protocol, Atlas is not just an application of Nebulas mainnet, it also supports the marketing and user adoption- not only Nebulas and our ecosystem, but also the entire blockchain industry.  Meanwhile, I personally have initiated Bitsclub Vision Program and the Public Chain Technology Alliance (PTCA) which already has over 20 partners in the entire public chain ecosystem. We hope that within PCTA, these projects can share technologies, developers community and other resources to jointly promote the ecosystem development and grow together.</p>  \n\n<p>Therefore, we always welcome and sincerely hope that our community would come and join us in the ecosystem development, because Nebulas is working hard to provide a fair and equal ecosystem for everyone to benefit and get value from their contributions. Go Nebulas!</p></r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'162.158.106.75',0,1),(168,16,51,'2019-01-11 09:53:36',119,'comment','<r><p><POSTMENTION discussionid=\"16\" displayname=\"DagCoin\" id=\"138\" number=\"43\" username=\"DagCoin\">@DagCoin#138</POSTMENTION> 钱包，交易所，DAPP，媒体很多平台都是流量入口，但每一项都面临着行业同一生态位上的充分竞争，需要持续的技术开发和运营投入。因此，星云链对钱包开发的态度是鼓励社区开发多样性的，侧重点不同的钱包，同时接入更多的第三方平台专业钱包平台，使得星云生态里的用户有更多种的选择。我们的NAS nano Pro以及网页钱包和插件等是给社区提供的钱包功能示例。事实上，社区已经开发了不少体验更好的钱包。有位国外开发者做的钱包插件在社区里要比官方的插件更受欢迎，激励计划涌现出的开发者最近也在进行星云移动钱包的开发，据我们了解，他们想整合星云链上的NRC20资产以及星云链上的dapp，这些行为我们都非常鼓励，并在技术和宣传上提供支持。同时市面上很多国内国外的三方钱包和正在和我们合作对接，我们对于钱包的合作一直保持开放，也欢迎大家多多对接星云的DApp和生态。另外，感谢你产品需求方面的建议，星云指数会在后续的版本中集成入NAS Nano Pro，也希望社区中三方钱包基于星云指数开发出更多有盈利场景可以持续获客的应用。</p>\n\n</r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'172.68.65.201',0,1),(169,31,1,'2019-01-11 10:32:56',64,'comment','<r><p>Post any tech suggestions, comments, thinking here. Don<FP char=\"’\">\'</FP>t be shy, we<FP char=\"’\">\'</FP>d love to hear the voice from the community.   For any specific issue/bug, a better place will be github.</p> </r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'108.162.226.38',0,1),(170,11,9,'2019-01-11 14:57:31',112,'comment','<t><p>Hi nice to e-me