healthy and sustainable Nebulas ecosystem !</p></r>','2019-01-23 02:59:11',109,NULL,NULL,'172.68.46.8',0,1),(236,49,2,'2019-01-23 02:58:12',84,'discussionStickied','{\"sticky\":true}',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1),(237,46,16,'2019-01-23 02:59:21',167,'comment','<r><p><USERMENTION displayname=\"Samuel\" id=\"64\" username=\"Samuel\">@Samuel</USERMENTION> , I am very grateful to you for what you have helped me. But when working with node nebulas I encountered some problems : <br/>\nWhen I create a testnet docker under the guidance of wiki nebulas, it generates an error.</p>\n<H1><s># </s>github.com/nebulasio/go-nebulas/nf/nbre</H1>\n<p>/usr/bin/ld: cannot find -lnbre_rt<br/>\ncollect2: error: ld returned 1 exit status<br/>\nmake: *** [build] Error 2<br/>\nMakefile:98: recipe for target <FP char=\"‘\">\'</FP>build<FP char=\"’\">\'</FP> failed<br/>\nThe command <FP char=\"‘\">\'</FP>/bin/sh -c make build<FP char=\"’\">\'</FP> returned a non-zero code: 2</p>\n</r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'172.68.253.158',0,1),(238,46,17,'2019-01-23 03:00:15',167,'comment','<r><H1><s># </s>Docker File testnet</H1>\n<p>FROM golang:1.9</p>\n\n<p>ARG VERSION=1.0.8.1</p>\n\n<p>RUN apt-get update<br/>\nRUN apt-get install -y build-essential checkinstall libgflags-dev libsnappy-dev zlib1g-dev libbz2-dev sudo git<br/>\nRUN cd /tmp &amp;&amp; git clone <URL url=\"https://github.com/facebook/rocksdb.git\">https://github.com/facebook/rocksdb.git</URL> &amp;&amp; cd rocksdb &amp;&amp; git checkout v5.13.1 &amp;&amp; make clean &amp;&amp; make install<br/>\nRUN go get -u github.com/golang/dep/cmd/dep</p>\n\n<p>RUN export GOPATH=/go<br/>\nRUN mkdir -p $GOPATH/src/github.com/nebulasio</p>\n\n<p>RUN cd $GOPATH/src/github.com/nebulasio &amp;&amp; git clone <URL url=\"https://github.com/nebulasio/go-nebulas\">https://github.com/nebulasio/go-nebulas</URL> &amp;&amp; cd go-nebulas &amp;&amp; git checkout testnet</p>\n\n<p>WORKDIR /go/src/github.com/nebulasio/go-nebulas/</p>\n\n<p>RUN make dep<br/>\nRUN make deploy-v8<br/>\nRUN make build</p>\n\n<p>COPY conf/* ./conf/default/</p>\n\n<p>EXPOSE 8684<br/>\nEXPOSE 8685<br/>\nEXPOSE 8888</p>\n\n<p>ENTRYPOINT [<FP char=\"“\">\"</FP>./neb<FP char=\"”\">\"</FP>, <FP char=\"“\">\"</FP>-c<FP char=\"”\">\"</FP>, <FP char=\"“\">\"</FP>conf/default/config.conf<FP char=\"”\">\"</FP>]</p></r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'172.68.253.158',0,1),(239,48,8,'2019-01-23 03:00:32',84,'comment','<r><p><POSTMENTION discussionid=\"48\" displayname=\"mook\" id=\"224\" number=\"5\" username=\"mook\">@mook#224</POSTMENTION> 不好意思 改过来啦</p></r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'162.158.59.37',0,1),(240,46,18,'2019-01-23 03:01:53',167,'comment','<r><H1><s># </s>The configuration file is located in the link below :<e> </e></H1>\n<p><URL url=\"https://github.com/nebulasio/go-nebulas/tree/testnet/testnet/conf\">https://github.com/nebulasio/go-nebulas/tree/testnet/testnet/conf</URL></p></r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'172.68.253.158',0,1),(241,46,19,'2019-01-23 08:40:23',64,'comment','<r><p><POSTMENTION discussionid=\"46\" displayname=\"uranus97s2\" id=\"240\" number=\"18\" username=\"uranus97s2\">@uranus97s2#240</POSTMENTION></p> \n\n<p>You need to build nbre firstly, a quick start is like this:</p>\n <LIST><LI><s>- </s>go to the <FP char=\"“\">\"</FP>nbre<FP char=\"”\">\"</FP> directory, and then: source prepare.sh</LI>\n <LI><s>- </s>if everything goes well during the preparation phase, then set up environment variables by: source env.set.sh</LI>\n <LI><s>- </s>create a directory <FP char=\"“\">\"</FP>build<FP char=\"”\">\"</FP> in the <FP char=\"“\">\"</FP>nbre<FP char=\"”\">\"</FP> directory, from the <FP char=\"“\">\"</FP>build<FP char=\"”\">\"</FP> directory: cmake ../; and then: make<br/>\n for more details, you may wanna refer to: <URL url=\"https://github.com/nebulasio/go-nebulas/tree/testnet/nbre\">https://github.com/nebulasio/go-nebulas/tree/testnet/nbre</URL></LI></LIST>\n\n<p>Please also notice that, since the nbre was just released on testnet, it<FP char=\"’\">\'</FP>s still under testing and development. We did not systematically test it on docker yet, so you may encounter some issues, if so, just let us know.</p></r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'141.101.85.164',0,1),(242,46,20,'2019-01-23 10:30:28',167,'comment','<r><p><POSTMENTION discussionid=\"46\" displayname=\"Samuel\" id=\"241\" number=\"19\" username=\"Samuel\">@Samuel#241</POSTMENTION>  Thank you again. But I still try to work on your way, because for me it<FP char=\"’\">\'</FP>s quite hard. can you share me a dockerfile testnet . I will be very grateful with you !</p></r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'172.68.253.110',0,1),(243,48,9,'2019-01-23 12:28:08',148,'comment','<r><p><EMAIL email=\"13696971792@139.com\">13696971792@139.com</EMAIL></p></r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'141.101.107.177',0,1),(244,20,37,'2019-01-23 20:40:47',153,'comment','<r><p>Thanks for the given anwers. My e-mail is <EMAIL email=\"nebulas1982@outlook.com\">nebulas1982@outlook.com</EMAIL></p></r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'141.101.104.218',0,1),(245,46,21,'2019-01-24 06:33:04',33,'comment','<r><p><POSTMENTION discussionid=\"46\" displayname=\"uranus97s2\" id=\"242\" number=\"20\" username=\"uranus97s2\">@uranus97s2#242</POSTMENTION> The current docker containing nbre environment is not ready yet, and we will support docker in the future.</p></r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'108.162.215.145',0,1),(246,46,22,'2019-01-24 06:53:30',167,'comment','<r><p><POSTMENTION discussionid=\"46\" displayname=\"larry\" id=\"245\" number=\"21\" username=\"larry\">@larry#245</POSTMENTION>  I made a successful private-testnet network. But what I want here is to be able to use the testnet network of nebulas. But when I follow the instructions of the nebulas with testnet network , it fails. My purpose is to be able to run testnet network. help me please!</p></r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'172.68.253.158',0,1),(247,46,23,'2019-01-24 12:00:02',33,'comment','<r><p><POSTMENTION discussionid=\"46\" displayname=\"uranus97s2\" id=\"246\" number=\"22\" username=\"uranus97s2\">@uranus97s2#246</POSTMENTION> As <POSTMENTION discussionid=\"46\" displayname=\"Samuel\" id=\"241\" number=\"19\" username=\"Samuel\">@Samuel#241</POSTMENTION> mentioned, you should first compile the nbre related dependencies. If your private network is based on the testnet branch, you can connect to the test network directly using testnet<FP char=\"’\">\'</FP>s configuration file. Test the network configuration file in <URL url=\"https://github.com/nebulasio/go-nebulas/blob/testnet/testnet/conf/config.conf\">https://github.com/nebulasio/go-nebulas/blob/testnet/testnet/conf/config.conf</URL>. <br/>\nThe Testnet details in <URL url=\"https://github.com/nebulasio/wiki/blob/master/testnet.md\">https://github.com/nebulasio/wiki/blob/master/testnet.md</URL>.</p>\n</r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'108.162.215.139',0,1),(248,50,1,'2019-01-25 03:02:02',168,'comment','<r><p>前不久，星云解散了微信的官方社群，只保留了开发者社群。并提供了星云邮件组和星云Wiki，作为官方对外沟通的渠道。</p>\n\n<p>不得不承认星云邮件组和星云Wiki是不错，内容很全面，定期有回复。</p>\n\n<p>但是作为星云链（Nebulas)的铁粉，呼喊有更接地气的沟通方式。</p>\n\n<p>有没有呢？<br/>\n答案是肯定的。</p>\n\n<QUOTE><i>&gt; </i><p>除了官方社群平台，星云还有一些第三方社区平台。这些平台活跃度高，有专门的人打点。小哥哥小姐姐贼热情，<br/>\n<i>&gt; </i>如果你是星云的铁粉，星云的支持者，加入这些社区平台，也是不错的选择。</p></QUOTE>\n\n<p>不多说，快到碗里来！！！</p>\n</r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'172.68.254.57',0,1),(249,50,2,'2019-01-25 03:04:34',168,'comment','<r><H3><s>### </s>星云铁头群</H3>\n\n<p>“星云铁头群”是星云最活跃的第三方社群，每天群里都有讨论，社群成员质量也相当高。群内潜伏有星云官方人员，时常回复社区问题，也是铁头群不公开的秘密。</p>\n\n<p><STRONG><s>**</s>何为“铁头”，就是对星云充满信仰，高度认同星云愿景，颠破不灭，铁打不烂。<e>**</e></STRONG></p>\n\n<p>正因如此，进入铁头群的门槛相当高，许多粉丝都以铁头成员为荣，群内成员常常满员，需要熟人引荐才能进入。</p>\n\n<QUOTE><i>&gt; </i><p>平台评价：五颗星</p></QUOTE></r>','2019-01-25 03:10:25',168,NULL,NULL,'172.68.254.57',0,1),(250,50,3,'2019-01-25 03:11:31',168,'comment','<r><H3><s>### </s>十元见粉丝群</H3>\n\n<p>“十元见”由星云社群传奇人物鱼面酱创办，人称鱼总。</p>\n\n<p>鱼面酱与星云官方联系密切，自2018年年中，相继在微信公众号“十元见”，推出多篇高质量的星云人物专访文章，包括星云研究院院长范学鹏博士，星云首席架构师陈聪明博士，星云研究总监王卓尔等重量级人物，并联合星云官方举办多场活动。现“十元见”包括自媒体公众号和十元见社群，已发展为星云社区一只重要的第三方力量。</p>\n\n<QUOTE><i>&gt; </i><p>评价：五颗星</p></QUOTE></r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'172.68.254.57',0,1),(251,50,4,'2019-01-25 03:14:47',168,'comment','<r><H3><s>### </s>星云链NebulasFans</H3>\n\n<p>星云链NebulasFans是微博平台，由星云粉丝创立，目前粉丝数在百人左右。鉴于星云未开通官方微博，星云链NebulasFans是星云在微博的头号宣传平台。</p>\n\n<p>参照其他项目社区微博粉丝，星云链NebulasFans未来的潜力会很大，也欢迎各位微博用户关注星云链NebulasFans。</p>\n\n<QUOTE><i>&gt; </i><p>评价：四颗星<br/>\n链接：<URL url=\"https://weibo.com/u/6467339283\"><s>[</s>星云链NebulasFans<e>](https://weibo.com/u/6467339283)</e></URL></p></QUOTE></r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'162.158.178.234',0,1),(252,50,5,'2019-01-25 03:16:39',168,'comment','<r><H3><s>### </s>星云链吧</H3>\n\n<p>百度贴吧是全球最大的中文社区，自然是许多人初识星云链的重要渠道。百度贴吧的好处是覆盖人群范围广，获取信息方便快捷。但信息的质量不高，在信息的有效性上是硬伤。</p>\n\n<p>星云链吧目前拥有418个粉丝，共发布了712个帖子。帖子信息时效性略显滞后，一个好的贴吧需要吧主时常打理，定期维护。本吧应该处于自发阶段。</p>\n\n<QUOTE><i>&gt; </i><p>评价：三颗星<br/>\n链接：<URL url=\"https://tieba.baidu.com/f?ie=utf-8&amp;kw=%E6%98%9F%E4%BA%91%E9%93%BE&amp;fr=search\"><s>[</s>星云链吧<e>](https://tieba.baidu.com/f?ie=utf-8&amp;kw=%E6%98%9F%E4%BA%91%E9%93%BE&amp;fr=search)</e></URL></p></QUOTE>\n</r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'172.68.253.110',0,1),(253,50,6,'2019-01-25 03:18:35',168,'comment','<r><H3><s>### </s>星云链中文社区</H3>\n\n<p>星云第三方论坛平台。根据论坛信息，星云链中文论坛，已经稳定运行了220天，内容也一直在更新。但是会员数偏少，仅有19名会员，12个帖子，没能得到很好的利用。</p>\n\n<p>相较于微信等社群，论坛有利于内容的沉淀，但在信息传播上不如社群灵活。貌似星云官方也意识到了这个问题，相继上线了新版的Wiki和星云官方社群论坛。这就让星云链中文社区的地位有些尴尬。</p>\n\n<p>以上就是目前主流的第三方星云平台，当然这些平台仅仅是中文平台。海外的平台也有很多，有机会再详细介绍。</p>\n\n<QUOTE><i>&gt; </i><p>评价：四颗星<br/>\n<i>&gt; </i>链接：<URL url=\"http://nasfans.org/\"><s>[</s>星云链中文社区<e>](http://nasfans.org/)</e></URL></p></QUOTE>\n</r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'172.68.253.110',0,1),(254,50,7,'2019-01-25 03:19:14',168,'comment','<r><H3><s>### </s>星云扁头群</H3>\n\n<p>星云扁头群，顾名思义就是头被打扁的星云粉丝社群。名字虽跟星云铁头群一字之差，但是无论是从活跃度上，还是群成员质量上，远远不如星云铁头群，呈现出冰火两重天的态势。</p>\n\n<QUOTE><i>&gt; </i><p>评价：三颗星</p></QUOTE>\n\n</r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'172.68.253.110',0,1),(255,50,8,'2019-01-25 03:20:23',168,'comment','<r><p><EM><s>_</s>以上就是笔者了解到的主流的第三方星云平台，也欢迎其他小伙伴进行补充，当然这些平台仅仅是中文平台。海外的平台也有很多，有机会再详细介绍。<e>_</e></EM></p>\n</r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'172.68.253.110',0,1),(256,50,9,'2019-01-25 03:48:51',116,'comment','<r><p><POSTMENTION discussionid=\"50\" displayname=\"weiht12\" id=\"249\" number=\"2\" username=\"weiht12\">@weiht12#249</POSTMENTION> 星云铁粉，想进群，求群号？</p></r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'172.68.143.249',0,1),(257,50,10,'2019-01-25 10:18:49',168,'comment','<r><p><POSTMENTION discussionid=\"50\" displayname=\"chenshiyan\" id=\"256\" number=\"9\" username=\"chenshiyan\">@chenshiyan#256</POSTMENTION> 微信群没有群号的，可以先关注已有的平台哈。</p></r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'162.158.178.198',0,1),(258,50,11,'2019-01-25 13:04:50',116,'comment','<t><p>想进星云开发者群？</p></t>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'162.158.59.37',0,1),(259,50,12,'2019-01-26 03:26:42',168,'comment','<r><p><POSTMENTION discussionid=\"50\" displayname=\"chenshiyan\" id=\"258\" number=\"11\" username=\"chenshiyan\">@chenshiyan#258</POSTMENTION> 添加星云群秘微信哈。</p></r>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'172.68.253.134',0,1),(260,44,2,'2019-01-26 18:14:21',31,'discussionTagged','[[13],[2,13,28]]',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1),(261,25,3,'2019-01-26 18:15:32',31,'discussionTagged','[[1,2],[1,2,28]]',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1),(262,51,1,'2019-01-26 18:20:21',31,'comment','<r><p><STRONG><s>**</s>DIP, Developer Incentive Protocol. <br/>\nProvide native on-chain incentive for developers.<e>**</e></STRONG><br/>\nReleased on Dec 31, 2018</p> \n\n<p>Incentives are the driving force of blockchain evolution. Nebulas Incentive (NI) includes Developer Incentive Protocol (DIP) and Proof of Devotion (PoD).<br/>\nDIP provides a positive feedback loop for developers to create high-quality decentralized applications.<br/>\nDIP will reward high ranking developers based on our open source Nebulas Rank (NR) algorithm. Rewards will be distributed in the form of Nebulas coin (NAS).</p>\n\n<p>Learn more about <URL url=\"https://nebulas.io/nova.html\"><s>[</s>Nebulas NOVA<e>](https://nebulas.io/nova.html)</e></URL>.<br/>\n<URL url=\"https://nebulas.io/docs/NebulasMauvepaper.pdf\"><s>[</s